      "title": "盘点目前NBA最赚的五笔交易,火箭、湖人、热火都在其中",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_331692d215341152",
      "snippet": "<p>在NBA这个充满智慧较量的舞台上,一笔精妙的操作往往能改变一支球队的命运｡它们或以最小的代价撬动巨大的战力,新赛季至今,联盟中已涌现出多笔令管理层同行们艳羡不已的“神操作”,让我们来盘点五笔堪称“赚翻”的交易与签约:</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.",
      "date": "2025-12-01 13:02:11"
    },
    {
      "title": "科里·亚历山大",
      "link": "https://baike.baidu.com/item/科里·亚历山大/19947043",
      "snippet": "科里·亚历山大(Cory Alexander),美国职业篮球运动员,在1995年NBA选秀中第1轮第29顺位被圣安东尼奥马刺队选中｡基本内容NBA数据 (参考资料) ",
      "date": "2024-04-08 08:19:24"
    },
    {
      "title": "קנה NBA 2K25 x WWE 2K24 Bundle  Xbox",
      "link": "https://www.xbox.com/he-IL/games/store/nba-2k25-x-wwe-2k24-bundle/9N448JMCBJLP/0010/B0FBK3Z3FMNS",
      "snippet": "2K • ספורט ממוטב עבור Xbox Series X|S ממוטב עבור Xbox Series X|S מפרסמים של משחקים שאתה מפעיל מקבלים גישה לפרטי הפרופיל שלך ב- Xbox ולנתונים שמשויכים לך, בזמן שאתה משחק. קבל מידע נוסף משחקים מרובי משתתפים מקוונים בקונסולה דורשים מינוי Xbox Game Pass Essential, Premium או Ultimate (המינויים נמכרים בנפרד). Take the court and enter the ring with this bundle that celebrates the best in sports gaming today. Experience all the hoop slamming, top-rope diving fun with this ultimate sports entertainment experience.Make history with NBA 2K25! Command every court with authenticity and realism powered by ProPLAY™*, delivering the most authentic NBA experience to date. Play as today’s greatest players, history's greatest legends, or define your own legacy in MyCAREER, MyTEAM, MyNBA, and The W*. Build your dynasty and transcend eras on your quest to beat the best, in order to be the best.WWE 2K24 celebrates the past, present, and future of sports entertainment, from WWE Legends “Stone Cold” Steve Au",
      "date": "2026-04-20 23:19:37"
    },
    {
      "title": "From Undrafted Player to Comeback: Isaac Jones' Journey to a Two-Year Contract_point_the_League",
      "link": "https://www.sohu.com/a/874848885_122328931",
      "snippet": "On March 23, 2025, the NBA court announced an inspiring piece of news: the Sacramento Kings declared that they would convert two-way contract center Isaac Jones' contract into a standard two-year NBA contract. This decision not only marks a major turning point in Jones' personal career but also reflects a typical pathway for NBA players at the lower tier to achieve success through the Development League. The Early Struggles: From Undrafted to G League Star Isaac Jones' professional journey did not start smoothly. As an undrafted player in the 2024 NBA Draft, he faced the predicament of having no team to play for. However, the Stockton G League team, affiliated with the Kings, provided him with an opportunity. In just 15 G League games, Jones showcased his skills by averaging 21.3 points, 9.7 rebounds, 1.7 assists, and 1.0 steals and blocks, boasting an impressive shooting percentage of 56.7%. This stellar performance quickly caught the attention of the Kings, ultimately leading to a tw",
      "date": "2025-03-23 21:37:00"
