      "snippet": "src='http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-55211287-4FE2DC1717A39774118E603FAFD1F233/0?</p><p>开拓者vs奇才</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-88581559-F2EB1598DD1E2B1DF102AEA9C12456B9/0?fmt=png&size=701&h=1804&w=1500&ppv=1' data-aigc-mark='0'/></p><p>布伦森28分3板4助,尼克斯轻取国王｡</p><p>鹈鹕vs雷霆</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-3995577567-28BFAE6BA0178F861F377890F3EEA693/0?",
